---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: stdout
---
A fast Rust CLI speedtest tool. (placeholder; under active development)

Usage: rspeed [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -d, --duration <DURATION>        Test duration in seconds [default: 10]
  -c, --connections <CONNECTIONS>  Parallel connections (1..=32) [default: 4]
  -s, --server <SERVER>            Custom server URL. Defaults to Cloudflare when unset
      --no-upload                  Skip the upload phase
      --no-download                Skip the download phase
  -f, --format <FORMAT>            Output format [default: human] [possible values: human, json, silent]
      --color <COLOR>              Color output mode [default: auto] [possible values: auto, always, never]
  -4, --ipv4                       Force IPv4
  -6, --ipv6                       Force IPv6
  -v, --verbose...                 Increase verbosity (-v, -vv, -vvv)
  -h, --help                       Print help
  -V, --version                    Print version
